2001;;Inferno;;British;;Paul Kousoulides;;Emily Booth, Sanjeev Bhaskar;;sci-fi;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inferno_(2001_short);;Set inside a "Quake" like video game, one of the game's cannon-fodder grunts falls for the Lara Croft-inspired heroine and, in a constantly looping game level, tries time and again to catch her attention before she can "chain gun" him.